tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All parameters are within normal limits except for a mildly elevated HbA1c (6.0%), indicating possible prediabetes or impaired glucose tolerance. Recommend clinical correlation and consideration of lifestyle modification or further evaluation for glycemic control. No evidence of renal or electrolyte disturbances.
